{"title":"活着的勇士  二大队二中队吕园子战斗片断","authors":["胡奇"],"dates":[{"year":1946,"month":9,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"活着的勇士"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二大队二中队吕园子战斗片断"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“流不干的河水呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱不光的歌；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"数不尽的高山呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说不尽的英雄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万年青，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千年红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"攻打吕园子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"数上张嘉荣。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼看着七个勇士跳过河沟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼看着七个勇士打入寨门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼看着反动派的火力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一阵比一阵紧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，七个勇士七个无比的英雄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个个倒下去又站起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站起来又倒下去。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切机枪都停了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切炮声都止了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄张嘉荣左腿打断了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他微微睁开眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看见身边六个同志握着枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"静静的躺在血泊里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“班长，班长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同志！同志！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们谁没有死啊？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快给我一颗炸弹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我打过去！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寨门里静静的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有半点声音。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人过留名，雁过留声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为人民战死最光荣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"突然，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪声响了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个炮弹在勇士身边开花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勇士赶紧抬起半个身子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的嘴角挂起一丝冷笑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“哼，反动派又干了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快把同志们丢下的武器收起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别让他们拿。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当他把七枝枪搂住的时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这活着的勇士，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却昏昏的又倒下去了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“同志你光荣负伤了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快把枪交给我吧。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“不，我不给，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是九连的枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可不该你拿！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“同志你忘了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是营教导员呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我姓方……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“啥，教导员？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勇士的喉咙给什么东西塞住了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他死死的盯着教导员，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好一阵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泪水才顺着那黄蜡蜡的脸腮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哗哗流下。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“同志，别难过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱队伍都冲上去了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人眼看就垮台。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活着的勇士，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忽然坐起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他抓起一枝枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘴里嚷着："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我也要去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要杀几个”……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勇士的腿再也站不起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的左腿真的给敌人打断了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活着的勇士被担架抬走了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"教导员紧握着他的手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他却忍着痛苦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放开眉头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“教导员同志，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给咱九连同志说呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请大家要保护好那七枝枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别忘了给死了的同志复仇！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胡奇"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}